rComments: One of the best classes I've taken! Very knowledgeable in the lecture material and is a fantastic lecturer. Very understanding of student life struggles. Relays expectations well, gives focused feedback and makes time for his students. Always on the look out for courses he is teaching

Lecturing skills are OK. Does his job but shows no enthusiasm in teaching. Looks like he's burned out from working multiple jobs all the time. Unnecessary group projects which one can easily finish on their own but have to put up with procratinating team members. And you'll get the same mark, yuk!

One of the best professors I have come across. Amazingly caring, takes care of student needs and very empathetic. His flexible approach towards assignments enables students to give out their best. Strong fundamentals in field of Process Mining, and very charismatic ! Balanced grading scheme involving group projects and alignments. Always Welcomin
